sub_title: Director Supply Chain Development Performance Management EMEA at adidas
summary:
Passionate champion of the digital revolution with a track record of working in retail, fashion, sporting goods industries across the globe. Deep experience in building and development e2e Omnichannel, eCommerce operational excellence environment.

Love to be in a fast paced, innovative and high risk environment surrounded by people who want to challenge each other and be challenged to maximize results. I am data driven but love working in the unknown and in creative.
